{"tid":1157083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜語出驚人「美國國務卿兼任外交部長」 鄉民崩潰：庾澄慶兼任哈林？","createTime":"2019-05-16T04:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T15:40:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":310,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"a91e5536c52f3de0ad7ae750b1da66698369c83e","tid":1157083,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜語出驚人「國務卿兼任外交部長」 鄉民崩潰：庾澄慶兼任哈林？<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜是2020超級熱門人選，近日接受《TVBS新聞》專訪，再次覺得若當總統，改在高雄上班不錯，且還想修憲讓總統本人兼行政院長。<br />\n<br />\n不料韓國瑜以美國舉例，「就是像美國一樣，美國有國務卿，事實上是外交部長，總統能不能兼行政院長？直接對行政院負責，有沒有這種可能？」<span style=\"color: red;\">這讓網友紛紛崩潰，認為韓國瑜比喻不倫不類，因為國務卿主力工作本來就是外交，並非兼任</span>，「庾澄慶兼任哈林？」、「老公也兼任你的配偶」、「國務卿不就是外交部長」、「國務卿的職務主外交啊，相當於外交部部長，所以他在說什麼？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2791872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2791872&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=f14f6ccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2791872&h=fe96d9b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2791872</a>"},{"pid":"c0d2ab7a3d37b66fcd919301177f300f240c7ccf","tid":1157083,"uid":35790,"like":288,"dislike":1,"score":287,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:31:57.000Z","msg":"台灣發大財"},{"pid":"c86557067df3c929e90e2014eb081f1fc04a509c","tid":1157083,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef6b921f7c4d782b711acc5c549c8540798c598","tid":1157083,"uid":77092,"like":126,"dislike":0,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"919cd8ca1cc19100ff91a9babcdb3324f6d2a4c6","tid":1157083,"uid":21917,"like":378,"dislike":0,"score":378,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"原來 哈林同庾澄慶個傳說係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"